      "name": "CPB inlet boundary condition dataset — v1",
      "description": "Physiological flow waveforms and pressure boundary conditions measured from in-vitro CPB circuit experiments. Includes pulsatile flow profiles at 3, 4, and 5 L/min for five rotational speed settings. These boundary conditions were collected and processed prior to the November 2025 model revision. The revision introduced updated near-wall turbulence treatment (k-omega SST with curvature correction); the dataset team assessed this change as not material to the inlet BC specification, as the waveform shapes and mean flow rates are independent of near-wall closure choices. Formal re-validation against the revised model was therefore deferred pending the next scheduled review cycle.",
      "dataVintage": "2025-10-10T14:30:00Z",
      "sourceOrganization": "https://uofa.net/synth/org/morrison-cardiovascular-lab"
