      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted at 4 L/min, 3000 RPM. GCI for normalized hemolysis index is 3.2%, satisfying the MRL 2 threshold. Coarse (2.1M), medium (5.8M), and fine (14.7M) cell counts used with consistent polyhedral topology."
