    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/morrison-cou1-cpb-decision",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The model is judged sufficient to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device. The inlet boundary condition dataset predates the November 2025 model revision by approximately three weeks; the team assessed the revision as not material to the dataset's applicability and proceeded without formal re-validation of the updated model against the existing dataset.",
